<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body { font-family: "SimSun", serif; }
    table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 1040px; }
    td, th { border: 1px solid #333; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: center; }
    .no-border { border: 0; }
    .company { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; height: 42px; }
    .title { font-size: 17px; text-align: center; height: 36px; }
    .meta { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; height: 32px; }
    .head { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; }
    .label { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; width: 130px; }
    .signature { font-family: "KaiTi", serif; font-size: 20px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table>
    <tr><td class="no-border company" colspan="7">省食供应链管理有限公司</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="no-border title" colspan="7">供应商报价比价选择表（2026年版）</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="no-border meta" colspan="7">时间：20260525　项目编码：XM202605250002　外部单号：PO-20260525-001　项目：冷链食材小批次采购　分类：食材　中标金额：¥12,100.00</td></tr>
    <tr class="head">
      <th>供应商</th>
      <th>联系人</th>
      <th>报价单编号</th>
      <th>项目内容</th>
      <th>项目报价</th>
      <th>业务员选择</th>
      <th>备注</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>宁波海味供应链</td>
      <td>王海</td>
      <td>BJ202605250001</td>
      <td>冷链食材供货，含配送</td>
      <td>¥12,100.00</td>
      <td>中标</td>
      <td>价格低，供货快</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>杭州鲜禾食品</td>
      <td>赵一鸣</td>
      <td>BJ202605250002</td>
      <td>冷链食材供货，含配送</td>
      <td>¥12,500.00</td>
      <td></td>
      <td>附件齐全</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>绍兴绿源食品</td>
      <td>林晓</td>
      <td>BJ202605250003</td>
      <td>冷链食材供货，含配送</td>
      <td>¥12,800.00</td>
      <td></td>
      <td></td>
    </tr>
    <tr><td>&nbsp;</td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">单位意见：</td><td colspan="6">同意按比价结果执行　<span class="signature">张经理</span></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">业务员意见：</td><td colspan="6">建议选择宁波海味供应链，报价金额最低且供货周期满足要求　<span class="signature">刘敏</span></td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">最终选择：</td><td colspan="6">宁波海味供应链有限公司</td></tr>
    <tr><td class="label">备注：</td><td colspan="6">本表字段固定，项目内容、项目报价、备注来自报价模板固定字段。</td></tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
